"title": "4303: metals",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4303",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Gold, silver, bronze, iron, copper, tin and lead are all mentioned in Scripture. Prized for their value, they were used in a variety of ways. Scripture uses as an image a metal refiner's fire for the purification of the lives of believers.</p>\n<h2>Gold</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job23:10\">JOB 23:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:10-Exod25:22\">EXO 25:10–25:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:21-Exod38:24\">EXO 38:21–38:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:27-1Kgs6:35\">1KI 6:27–6:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:48-1Kgs7:50\">1KI 7:48–7:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:14-1Kgs10:21\">1KI 10:14–10:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:7-Ps19:11\">PSA 19:7–19:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:18\">REV 3:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev17:4\">REV 17:4</a></p>\n<h2>Silver</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps12:6\">PSA 12:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:26-Gen37:28\">GEN 37:26–37:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:25-Exod38:28\">EXO 38:25–38:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:26-2Chr9:27\">2CH 9:26–9:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:72\">PSA 119:72</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:3-Matt27:10\">MAT 27:3–27:10</a></p>\n<h2>Bronze</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:22\">GEN 4:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod27:1-Exod27:7\">EXO 27:1–27:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:29-Exod38:31\">EXO 38:29–38:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:31-Num16:40\">NUM 16:31–16:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:9-2Chr4:18\">2CH 4:9–4:18</a></p>\n<h2>Iron</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut3:11\">DEU 3:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:7-Deut8:9\">DEU 8:7–8:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg4:2-Judg4:3\">JDG 4:2–4:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job40:15-Job40:18\">JOB 40:15–40:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:19\">EZK 27:19</a></p>\n<h2>Copper</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job28:2\">JOB 28:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:41-Mark12:44\">MRK 12:41–12:44</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:1-Luke21:4\">LUK 21:1–21:4</a></p>\n<h2>Tin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:12\">EZK 27:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:18\">EZK 22:18</a></p>\n<h2>Lead</h2>\n<h3>It was an exceptionally heavy metal</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:10\">EXO 15:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech5:5-Zech5:8\">ZEC 5:5–5:8</a></p>\n<h3>It was refined before use</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:29\">JER 6:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:21-Num31:23\">NUM 31:21–31:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:18-Ezek22:20\">EZK 22:18–22:20</a></p>\n<h3>Inscriptions were sometimes made on lead</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:23-Job19:24\">JOB 19:23–19:24</a></strong></p>\n<h3>It was traded between nations</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:12\">EZK 27:12</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The value of metals</h2>\n<h3>All metals were of value</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:8\">JOS 22:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr18:10\">1CH 18:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:14\">1CH 22:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:1-1Chr29:7\">1CH 29:1–29:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:11-Rev18:12\">REV 18:11–18:12</a></p>\n<h3>The relative value of metals</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:17\">ISA 60:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:21\">1KI 10:21</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:20\">2CH 9:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:25-1Kgs14:28\">1KI 14:25–14:28</a></p>\n<h2>Trade with metals</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:22\">1KI 10:22</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:21\">2CH 9:21</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:28\">GEN 37:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:11\">1KI 10:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:14-1Kgs10:15\">1KI 10:14–10:15</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:13-2Chr9:14\">2CH 9:13–9:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:48\">1KI 22:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:13\">EZK 27:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:22\">EZK 27:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:11\">ZEP 1:11</a></p>\n<h2>Idols were often made from various metals</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:4\">LEV 19:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:9\">1KI 14:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:19\">PSA 106:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:5\">ISA 48:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:22-Dan5:23\">DAN 5:22–5:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:8\">DAN 11:8</a></p>\n<h2>The refining of metals as an image of purification</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:10\">ISA 48:10</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:2\">MAL 3:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps12:6\">PSA 12:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech13:9\">ZEC 13:9</a></p>",
